As of the census<ref name="GR2">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]] |accessdate=January 31, 2008 |title=U.S. Census website }}</ref> of 2000, there were 865 people, 371 households, and 234 families residing in the town. By the [[2010 United States census|2010 census]], its population grew to 1,088; in 2020, its population was 1,235.

